install docker 
---------------------------------------
Step3: Initialize docker swarm & get the join token for workers.
Cmd: #docker swarm init
-------------------------------------------
Step4:Copy the join token of the worker nodes from manager node and paste individually to worker nodes to join. 
Worker node1
worker node2
worker node3
------------------------------------------------
Step5: Check whether all the worker nodes are connected to swarm or not.
Cmd:#docker node ls
**in manager node
-------------------------------------------------
Step6: Perform docker swarm operations
Create service and assign task to worker nodes
Cmd : #docker service create --replicas 5 alpine ping www.google.com
----------------------------------------------------
Step7: check docker service is created or not
COMMAND : ~#docker service ls
